  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="6473435">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/6473435/" class="title-link">哈扎尔拼图</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-6473435"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/ringying/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/user_normal.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/ringying/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">[已注销]</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2013-12-22"
      class="main-meta">2013-12-22 23:09:45</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_6473435_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  《哈扎尔辞典》的故事按照时间线回溯，最初始于创世纪，主角是上帝和魔鬼。  上帝的语言是动词，即“逻各斯、法律、规则、操行以及具体行为的保证”，这一切的发生均先于世界的创造；名词则是在这个世界之后创造出来的，旨在指称世界的万物。所以辞典中说“我们的语言有两种属...

