  </div>

      
  



  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="1002830">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/1002830/" class="title-link">夢的拼貼</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-1002830"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/misty/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u1002927-1.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/misty/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">阿霧</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2005-08-18"
      class="main-meta">2005-08-18 15:47:51</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_1002830_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  哈扎爾是一個在拜占庭時代存在的王國，《哈扎爾辭典》一直記錄這個曾經存在的沒落王國的歷史。當時由於國王發了一個夢，他召見了三大宗教派系的領袖，分別是基督教、伊斯蘭教和猶太教的使者前來解夢，誰解得最準確哈扎爾便歸順於哪個宗教，結果展開了哈扎爾大辯論，後來哈扎爾...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/1002830/#comments">(10回应)</a>
